over-oct-7-probe/0000018c-da32-d751-ad8d-ffb60f1e0000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦总理致欧盟高级官员：援助加沙防止大规模移民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-pm-to-senior-eu-officials-aid-gaza-to-prevent-mass-migration/0000018c-d9f8-d751-ad8d-fffc90db0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦官员担心加沙地带日益不适宜居住的灾难性状况将导致大规模逃亡。他们声称以色列打算采取国际医疗举措来减少人口</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 15:27:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-pm-to-senior-eu-officials-aid-gaza-to-prevent-mass-migration/0000018c-d9f8-d751-ad8d-fffc90db0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部阿拉伯城市男子遭枪击身亡；北部一女子被发现车内已无生命体征</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/man-fatally-shot-in-arab-city-in-central-israel-woman-found-lifeless-in-car-in-north/0000018c-d957-d751-ad8d-fff732600000</link><description>枪击事件中尚未逮捕任何嫌疑人 ■ 警方正在调查该女子的死亡，并调查可能的性侵犯和谋杀</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 12:14:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/man-fatally-shot-in-arab-city-in-central-israel-woman-found-lifeless-in-car-in-north/0000018c-d957-d751-ad8d-fff732600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长们公开反对 10 月 7 日对军队行为进行的内部调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-come-out-against-team-set-to-probe-armys-conduct-on-october-7/0000018c-d91c-ddba-abad-dbbd845b0000</link><description>以色列部长们猛烈抨击陆军参谋长领导对哈马斯袭击失败的调查。 “我们正处于战争之中，而你现在就开始调查？”有人说</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 11:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ministers-come-out-against-team-set-to-probe-armys-conduct-on-october-7/0000018c-d91c-ddba-abad-dbbd845b0000</guid></item><item><title>他的基布兹宣布，以色列人质于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-killed-on-october-7-body-being-held-in-gaza-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-d8ea-d751-ad8d-ffee89ab0000</link><description>塔米尔·阿达尔 (Tamir Adar) 是亚法·阿达尔 (Yaffa Adar) 的孙子，亚法·阿达尔 (Yaffa Adar) 也曾在加沙被哈马斯扣押，并通过人质交易获释。战争爆发以来，加沙132名人质中的26名人质已确认死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 10:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-killed-on-october-7-body-being-held-in-gaza-his-kibbutz-announces/0000018c-d8ea-d751-ad8d-ffee89ab0000</guid></item><item><title>随着反对以色列民主的政变停止，推翻内塔尼亚胡的战斗即将来临</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/we-are-well-into-the-day-before-israels-war-in-gaza-ends/0000018c-d626-d751-ad8d-ffa636ef0000</link><description>这位首相的毒药机器在10月7日之后沉寂了几天，现在在他试图保住职位时又恢复了全速运转。他的司法部长亚里夫·莱文（Yariv Levin）仍在继续他的谎言、半真半假和煽动行为</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:00:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/we-are-well-into-the-day-before-israels-war-in-gaza-ends/0000018c-d626-d751-ad8d-ffa636ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府在北部的承诺可能会让军事力量成为唯一选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-governments-promises-in-north-could-leave-military-force-as-the-only-option/0000018c-d60e-ddba-abad-d6af72280000</link><description>以色列承诺改变北部局势可能会将其推向更广泛的军事对抗 ■ 真主党对哈马斯高级官员被杀的强硬反应将使双方误判</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 04:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-governments-promises-in-north-could-leave-military-force-as-the-only-option/0000018c-d60e-ddba-abad-d6af72280000</guid></item><item><title>八枚火箭从黎巴嫩发射；哈马斯领导人呼吁布林肯制止以色列的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-live/israeli-army-establishes-team-to-investigate-hamas-october-7-attacks/0000018c-d781-daf6-a5df-d7fd37c00000</link><description>真主党主席在周五的讲话中警告阿鲁里被杀，以色列北部响起了火箭警报。 ■ 他的基布兹称，以色列人质塔米尔·阿达尔于 10 月 7 日被谋杀。与以色列国防军领导人就 10 月 7 日的军队调查发生冲突 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵被杀；至少 133 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 22,600 人死亡，57,910 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 02:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-live/israeli-army-establishes-team-to-investigate-hamas-october-7-attacks/0000018c-d781-daf6-a5df-d7fd37c00000</guid></item><item><title>即使在哈马斯的囚禁中，她也照亮了整个房间：卡梅尔·盖特仍然在加沙被扣为人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-in-captivity-she-lights-up-the-room-carmel-gat-is-still-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018c-d6a1-ddba-abad-d6a1ba470000</link><description>卡梅尔·盖特以其非凡的力量和决心而闻名。与她一起被哈马斯囚禁的人质说，她通过瑜伽和冥想课程帮助他们保持理智。她的许多朋友要求不要把她抛在后面</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 23:34:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-in-captivity-she-lights-up-the-room-carmel-gat-is-still-held-hostage-by-hamas/0000018c-d6a1-ddba-abad-d6a1ba470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列没有实施种族灭绝，但它有种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-isnt-committing-a-genocide-but-it-has-genocidaires/0000018c-d643-daf6-a5df-d77fccc00000</link><description>以色列的行动旨在摧毁哈马斯这个组织，而不是加沙的巴勒斯坦人民。真正让我担心的是以色列政界人士中担任弥赛亚派的高级职位，他们认为这场战争是犹太人民昭然命运的实现</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 22:06:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-05/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-isnt-committing-a-genocide-but-it-has-genocidaires/0000018c-d643-daf6-a5df-d77fccc00000</guid></item><item><title>“28 岁时，我被赶出了美国。我必须在日本和以色列之间做出选择”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-05/ty-article/.highlight/i-was-kicked-out-of-america-when-i-was-28-i-had-to-choose-between-japan-and-israel/0000018c-d646-daf6-a5df-d77e9a100000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一名日本人和一名美国人来到以色列在战争中表示支持和志愿服务</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 22:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-01-05/ty-article/.highlight/i-was-kicked-out-of-america-when-i-was-28-i-had-to-choose-between-japan-and-israel/0000018c-d646-daf6-a5df-d77e9a100000</guid></item><item><title>炸毁数百万美元：摩萨德对哈马斯和真主党资金的秘密战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blowing-up-millions-of-dollars-the-mossads-secret-war-on-hamas-and-hezbollah-funds/0000018c-d5af-daf6-a5df-d7ff58b30000</link><description>多年来，乌迪·利维领导摩萨德的一个部门，负责监控恐怖组织的资金流向。该部队凭借创造性的方法和几乎没有任何限制，成功阻止了向哈马斯和真主党转移巨额资金。然后就被关掉了</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:58:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/blowing-up-millions-of-dollars-the-mossads-secret-war-on-hamas-and-hezbollah-funds/0000018c-d5af-daf6-a5df-d7ff58b30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方要求受害者和目击者就哈马斯性暴力问题作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ask-victims-and-witnesses-to-testify-about-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-d580-d751-ad8d-ffa4acf40000</link><description>10月7日哈马斯性暴力事件的大多数受害者被杀害、被扣为人质或处于心理困扰状态而无法作证。以色列警方调查人员现呼吁公众鼓励活着的受害者或目击者与他们联系并提供证据</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:51:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ask-victims-and-witnesses-to-testify-about-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018c-d580-d751-ad8d-ffa4acf40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事情报局局长：我们可以打击“从加沙到伊朗”的敌人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-intelligence-chief-we-can-strike-our-enemies-from-gaza-to-iran/0000018c-d5e4-daf6-a5df-d7fc29410000</link><description>哈马斯一名高级官员在贝鲁特因以色列袭击而被暗杀后，阿哈龙·哈利瓦少将在讲话中告诉情报官员课程的新毕业生“永远表达你的专业意见”。始终、无处不在、针对任何级别或梯队”</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:33:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-military-intelligence-chief-we-can-strike-our-enemies-from-gaza-to-iran/0000018c-d5e4-daf6-a5df-d7fc29410000</guid></item><item><title>“此刻同情更重要”：以色列抗议艺术家受到人质的启发</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/compassion-is-more-important-now-the-israeli-protest-artist-inspired-by-the-hostages/0000018c-d4f0-daf6-a5df-d7fcdcc00000</link><description>泽夫·恩格尔梅尔 (Zeev Engelmayer) 最出名的是他饰演的激进分子肖什克 (Shoshke)，直到 10 月 7 日，肖什克都是反政府抗议活动中的常见人物。不过，自黑色星期六以来，他每天都画明信片，反映他对战争的希望和恐惧，尤其是哈马斯扣押的人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/compassion-is-more-important-now-the-israeli-protest-artist-inspired-by-the-hostages/0000018c-d4f0-daf6-a5df-d7fcdcc00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列选择英国法律专家在国际法院种族灭绝案中代表以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-chooses-british-legal-expert-to-represent-it-in-icj-genocide-case/0000018c-d5e5-d751-ad8d-ffe5b4880000</link><description>以色列法律专家表示，马尔科姆·肖教授必须辩称，以色列实际上遵守了国际法，以色列领导人的极端言论并不反映加沙的官方政策</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 20:01:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-chooses-british-legal-expert-to-represent-it-in-icj-genocide-case/0000018c-d5e5-d751-ad8d-ffe5b4880000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，自 10 月 7 日以来失踪的三名以色列人被绑架到加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/three-israeli-civilians-missing-since-october-7-were-kidnapped-to-gaza-idf-says/0000018c-d5ee-ddba-abad-d7effb590000</link><description>三名被绑架的以色列人被确认为 56 岁的伊兰·韦斯 (Ilan Weiss)、来自特拉维夫的 42 岁的哈南·亚布隆卡 (Hanan Yablonka) 和 28 岁的伊丹·什蒂维 (Idan Shtivi)</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 19:45:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-04/ty-article/three-israeli-civilians-missing-since-october-7-were-kidnapped-to-gaza-idf-says/0000018c-d5ee-ddba-abad-d7effb590000</guid></item><item><title>你不会通过否认哈马斯强奸以色列人来解放巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-04/ty-article/.highlight/you-wont-free-palestine-by-denying-hamas-raped-israelis/0000018c-d582-ddba-abad-d7a3d6510000</link><description>你可以拆开每个证人的证词，手摇每一个被剥光尸体的视频，并告诉每个愿意听的人，哈马斯不会这样做。但这不会抹去受害者在最后一刻所遭受的苦难，也不会解放巴勒斯坦</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 19:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-04/ty-article/.highlight/you-wont-free-palestine-by-denying-hamas-raped-israelis/0000018c-d582-ddba-abad-d7a3d6510000</guid></item></channel></rss>